description:
In this festive video, I'm singing the classic Christmas song "The First Noel" (karaoke version!) for you all to enjoy!

For the holidays, why not add a little Christmas cheer by watching this karaoke version of The First Noel? I hope you enjoy singing along with me! Merry Christmas and happy holidays!
Motion Graphics Used : Gospel Productions by Joe Hackney
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVBPHYusk0Jd2dMPqmq7CZw
Music by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters Karaoke Youtube Production.
